==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gunnel
<hw>Gun"nel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Gunwale</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A gunwale.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small, eel-shaped, marine fish
of the genus <gen>Mur⟦ae⟧noides</gen>; esp., <spn>M. gunnellus</spn> of
Europe and America; -- called also <altname>gunnel fish</altname>,
<altname>butterfish</altname>, <altname>rock eel</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gunner</ent>⟦br⟧
